            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<h1>Presentatie 16-11-2021</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://stichtingcarmelcollege.sharepoint.com/:p:/s/HHH_3hoek/ERd6FuX1mJ9CokQrlNMWC2cBI0lKJwEw7sdoVetYqgpFQQ?e=3fa7zo\">20211116 leermateriaal stadion.pptx</a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h1>Voorbereiding worldcaf\u00e9 17-11-2021</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://stichtingcarmelcollege.sharepoint.com/:w:/s/HHH_3hoek/EUy5VI95gWdHjO7zQewa_7kB7P2eNXRwgJMx1zp4V1RrBw?e=RIH9Ef\">Input Het Hooghuis worldcafe leermiddelen.docx</a></p>\n"
